======================================================
                Data.csv
======================================================

Information about the data fields saved

---------------------------------------------------
origin_url : Course page URL
----------------------------------------------------
department_id : department as present in the URL
department : Department name
----------------------------------------------------
course_id : Course id or number as savved by MIT
course : Course name
-----------------------------------------------------
These 3 fields are filled as from page https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/find-by-topic/
Topic :
sub_category :
specialty : 
-----------------------------------------------------------
download_size : Course materials size
download_url : Course material download path
-----------------------------------------------------------

============================================================


The script data_size.py tells you about the total dowload size : It is 16.41 GB

------------------------------------------------------------


The script pdf_extractor.py will extract the lecture or relevant pdfs from course materials download link.
This script will create a folder with the name of the course-id and store all the pdfs inside it.

To generate the the dataset just run :python pdf_extractor.py

============================================================
